    "final_verdict": "Dashpers shows promising potential but requires refinement before being enterprise-ready. Recommendations: 1) Streamline the technical architecture and resolve current limitations, 2) Add security and compliance considerations, 3) Develop clear market positioning and ROI metrics, 4) Create a professional demo and documentation, 5) Focus on core features before expanding scope. The project scores 6.5/10 overall, demonstrating good potential but needing significant development to become a viable enterprise solution. Its strongest aspects are its practical application and innovative approach, while its main areas for improvement are technical robustness and professional presentation."
